#ChatFuncions


###Functions inside the specific chat

-Abillity to send images.
-Abillity to send messages.
-Abillity to chose a smiley and send it.


###Functions in the Sign in page

-Send the Id and Password to check if the account is valid.
-Abillity to sign up.

###Functions in the Sign up page

-Validation of the information before signing up.
-Checking if there is no existing account.
-Signing up button.

###Functions in the List users and groups

-Add a new user to the list.
-Create a new group chat.
-Option to select a specific user's chat , then gather all the information from the server(chat history)
-Option to select a specific group's chat , then gather all the infromation from the server(chat history)





